'''Havaianas'''是一個由Scotsman Robert Fraser於1962年創建的[[巴西|巴西]]人字拖鞋品牌，該品牌目前由巴西製造公司Alpargatas擁有。其名稱Hava-{}-ianas一詞來自[[葡萄牙語|葡萄牙語]]的“[[夏威夷人|夏威夷人]]”。

在受到日本{{Link-ja|草履|草履}}鞋設計的啟發後，Fraser首創以[[橡膠|橡膠]]量產[[人字拖|人字拖]]。<ref name="IMD Business School">{{cite web|url=http://www.imd.org/research/challenges/TC062-09.cfm|title=Growth - How Havaianas Became a Global Brand.|accessdate=August 28, 2012|publisher=[[International_Institute_for_Management_Development|International Institute for Management Development]]|archive-date=2016-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161016211045/http://www.imd.org/research/challenges/TC062-09.cfm|dead-url=no}}</ref>最初，所有的Havaianas拖鞋之樣式皆為白色內底加上彩色外底與鞋帶。由於其簡約設計與低廉價格，這些拖鞋在巴西社會底層之間廣受歡迎。<ref name="CNBC Business">{{cite web|url=http://www.cnbcmagazine.com/story/brazils-rubber-soul/919/1/|title=Brazil's Rubber Soul.|accessdate=August 28, 2012|publisher=CNBC Magazine|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830153549/http://www.cnbcmagazine.com/story/brazils-rubber-soul/919/1|archivedate=2011年8月30日}}</ref>

1994年，其製造商為呼應流行風潮發表了八款稱作Hava-{}-ianas Top的單色拖鞋。此後，該品牌之產品方開始流行於巴西社會地位較高者之間。<ref name="Associated Press">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-2178801/As-Havaianas-celebrates-half-century-rubber-flip-flop-Brazils-famous-export.html/|title=As Havaianas celebrates half a century, how the rubber flip flop became Brazil's most famous export.|accessdate=August 28, 2012|newspaper=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|archive-date=2017-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224230931/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-2178801/As-Havaianas-celebrates-half-century-rubber-flip-flop-Brazils-famous-export.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>1998年，隨著即將在法國舉行的[[FIFA世界杯|FIFA世界杯]]，Havaianas推出了一系列在鞋帶上飾有縮小巴西國旗圖樣的人字拖鞋，以表明對巴西隊的支持。<ref name="Havaianas USA">{{cite web|url=http://usa.havaianas.com/en-US/about-havaianas/history/|title=About Havaianas/History.|accessdate=August 28, 2012|publisher=Havaianas USA|archive-date=2013-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130916185304/http://usa.havaianas.com/en-US/about-havaianas/history/|dead-url=no}}</ref>   現在，Havaianas拖鞋經常可以在海邊活動用品店等通路購得。<ref name="Cain_Kathryn">{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/features/the-timeline-flipflops-2039012.html|title=The Timeline: Flip-flops.|last=Cain|first=Kathryn|date=July 30, 2010|newspaper=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|accessdate=July 19, 2012|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925035522/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/features/the-timeline-flipflops-2039012.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

